{"tid":1981141,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"59歲 三高 甩左半隻牙","createTime":"2020-04-20T13:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T15:42:51.000Z","uid":153356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2262d2841ff75d7a235b00ba225fe7071ce9dd8b","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:17:32.000Z","msg":"家母有日食食下野甩左半隻牙<br />\n去左照x光<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Omg8Axc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmg8Axc.png&h=dcd5c034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n牙醫敲佢隻牙會病<br />\n話隻牙除左崩之外仲裂/斷開<br />\n話一定要剝<br />\n<br />\n睇左另一個醫生就話可以試下牙套（補牙？佢2個都有提過，唔知係咪同一樣野）<br />\n會有有30%成功 咁就唔洗剝同植<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁既情況 有冇牙醫ching可以比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2樣都咁貴唔想做完牙套低衰左最尾都係要剝牙<br />\n家母自己就好唔想剝 佢超怕痛又上左年紀<br />\n<br />\n順便問埋剝完醫生話做植牙會好過做牙橋 <br />\n請問係唔係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPs 植牙要成2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce47858856f234dd21f6e60664b977b0cb502b67","tid":1981141,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"出去問牙醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec642bb4035b1c7807144b90421ad18400ca51b","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce47858856f234dd21f6e60664b977b0cb502b67","tid":1981141,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"出去問牙醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"搵左2個<br />\n2個講既野都幾唔同<br />\n想睇下有冇其他人比到意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1d6d6b2d090cebd355f940af21b393fa9cb2d7","tid":1981141,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ec642bb4035b1c7807144b90421ad18400ca51b","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce47858856f234dd21f6e60664b977b0cb502b67","tid":1981141,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"出去問牙醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"搵左2個<br />\n2個講既野都幾唔同<br />\n想睇下有冇其他人比到意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"你咪問多幾個問到話唔整都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你根本唔想整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894016675fef2e95faf515b00eecf6ea3c544a47","tid":1981141,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"補牙唔係痛過剝牙咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5950dec3eb79cc40c7d288e04a4606e046bb852","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"睇x-ray就已經見到爛得好緊要，唔剝嘅話就要杜牙根加牙套，不過成功率唔高。因為咬爆咬裂嘅牙都係好難預計。<br />\n杜牙根加牙套講緊已經萬幾蚊，仲要成功率好低，最後都係要剝。<br />\n呢度見啲骨都唔差，鼻竇唔算好低，種牙就應該風險唔高。<br />\n不過齋睇X-ray而無真實睇過又好難下定論<br />\n<br />\n利申：牙醫"},{"pid":"c63d8504c9c8aabf98b15dc4271265a847504eac","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"btw, 隻智慧齒都應該有問題<br />\n同埋要洗牙，好多牙石"},{"pid":"58272fcb750204c3be25c8e3cce8c8546c391f62","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63d8504c9c8aabf98b15dc4271265a847504eac","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"btw, 隻智慧齒都應該有問題<br />\n同埋要洗牙，好多牙石"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"隻智慧齒佢話佢冇feel到痛過<br />\n所以暫時唔理佢住 整左依家果隻先<br />\n洗牙我會捉多d佢去㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢成日都話痛唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167426e09eafd3733fc9edf8d3ab5c57d9009893","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5950dec3eb79cc40c7d288e04a4606e046bb852","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"睇x-ray就已經見到爛得好緊要，唔剝嘅話就要杜牙根加牙套，不過成功率唔高。因為咬爆咬裂嘅牙都係好難預計。<br />\n杜牙根加牙套講緊已經萬幾蚊，仲要成功率好低，最後都係要剝。<br />\n呢度見啲骨都唔差，鼻竇唔算好低，種牙就應該風險唔高。<br />\n不過齋睇X-ray而無真實睇過又好難下定論<br />\n<br />\n利申：牙醫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"Thx ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽完你意見 諗住搵多個牙醫睇埋先判斷<br />\n聽落去似剝完植會保險d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇好牙醫推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c730acbe143bf71a9fa9084ec08752acd147b2","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58272fcb750204c3be25c8e3cce8c8546c391f62","tid":1981141,"uid":153356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c63d8504c9c8aabf98b15dc4271265a847504eac","tid":1981141,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:30:15.000Z","msg":"btw, 隻智慧齒都應該有問題<br />\n同埋要洗牙，好多牙石"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:06:36.000Z","msg":"隻智慧齒佢話佢冇feel到痛過<br />\n所以暫時唔理佢住 整左依家果隻先<br />\n洗牙我會捉多d佢去㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢成日都話痛唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThx ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"痛先洗就收得皮"},{"pid":"a46477b0d1a6